---------------------------------------------------------------------------
USING/COPYING

  KNXinstaller is distributed under the GNU General Public License
  (GPL). The rules for using and copying KNXinstaller are explained
  in the file COPYING.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
SUMMARY

  KNXinstaller is a GUI for installing KANOTIX (http://www.kanotix.com).
  It's made in C++ with KDevelop3 and it uses Qt and the Kanotix-
  Installer-Shellscript by Kano.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
FILE CONTENTS

  COPYING         GNU General Public License
  INSTALL         Instructions on how to install
  README          The file you are reading
  src/            The source files needed to compile KNXinstaller
  doc/            Documentation for KNXinstaller

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALLATION

  Read the file INSTALL, or load doc/install.html into your favorite
  web client, for instructions on how to install KNXinstaller.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
DOCUMENTATION

  Documentation for KNXinstaller is located in the doc/ directory.

